<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1943-03-13T16:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1943-03-13T16:00:00-05:00" n="245" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d245">
                    <note rend="inline" type="source">852.48/1444: Telegram</note>
                    <head>
                        <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in Spain</hi> (<persName type="from"><hi rend="italic">Hayes</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                        </hi>
                    </head>
                    <opener>
                        <dateline rendition="#right">
                            <placeName>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Madrid</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1943-03-13T22:00:00+01:00">March 13,
                                1943—10 p.m.</date>
                            <lb/> [Received March 14—3:45 p.m.]</dateline>
                    </opener>
                    <p>608. My 576, March 10, midnight. Rapidly increasing proportions of refugee
                        relief problem make it extremely difficult even approximately to estimate
                        future needs but it now appears that Embassy requirements for next 30 days
                        will exceed $150,000.</p>
                    <closer>
                        <signed>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Hayes</hi>
                        </signed>
                    </closer>
                </div>
                </body></text></TEI>